\verb{CR*} for \code{zeroinfl} / \code{hurdle} via \code{sandwich::vcovCL}, covering \strong{both
components} with one estimator. \verb{HC*} is refused (no hatvalues
machinery). For \code{glmmTMB}, see \link{table_regression_mixed}.
